text: Nestled in the serene Birchwood neighborhood, this 3 bed, 2.5 bath home on corner lot offers a blend of comfort and modern amenities. Entry features built-ins for ample storage. Enjoy outdoors in beautifully landscaped, newly fenced yard with a private patio, grassy area & raised beds in the front yard. Endless options! Many uses for this home. Live in 1 and rent the other, rent both or easily combine them to create 1 home. Lake view sunsets from your expansive deck are beckoning!
